###

## Get All Products
GET {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

###

## Get My Products (Protected - requires JWT)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

## Get Product by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/4
Content-Type: application/json

###

## Update Product (Protected - requires JWT + ownership)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/products/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Product Name",
  "description": "Updated description"
}

###

## Delete Product (Protected - requires JWT + ownership)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/products/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

## List Variants for Product
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/1/variants
Content-Type: application/json

